Guided Inquiry: Advanced Css

-Graded problems from the R2H program focusing on page manipulation with
  - Flex
  - Grid
  - Media Queries

Problem #1
  - Create an 8x8 checkerboard with alternating black and white squares
Problem #2
  -Create American flag using a img to represent the stars section
    -(Img should contain all 50 stars)
Problem #3
  - Create a store catalog page where :
    - There are two rows of products
    - Totaling 8 products
    - Where each product contains a:
      - Title
      - Price
      - Image
      - Short description
      - A link to a products page on a real website
Problem #4
  - Complete the Introduction to Responsive Web Design Challenges on Code Academy
    Link: https://www.freecodecamp.org/learn/responsive-web-design/responsive-web-design-principles/
